==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Tice
<hw>Tice</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Cricket)</fld> <def>A ball bowled to
strike the ground about a bat's length in front of the wicket.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

